Package: connectedness
Type: Package
Title: Connectedness Metrics for Genetic Evaluation Across Management Units
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Alan", "", email = "alan@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Computes connectedness metrics between management units (MUs)
    in animal breeding data under the contrast approach via Mixed Model
    Equations (MME). The package implements Coefficient of Determination
    (CD contrast) and Prediction Error Variance of Differences (PEVD contrast),
    and supports pedigree-based, genomic, and single-step relationship
    structures through A-inverse, G-inverse, and H-inverse matrices, as well
    as user-supplied inverse kernels. It also supports temporal restrictions
    and overlap summaries between management units.
